SGH Cyan (Blue): #009CDF (A bright, trustworthy medical blue)

SGH Green: #39B54A (A vibrant, natural "growth" green)

Charcoal Text: #373F47 (A dark, slate grey used for the main English text)

Gradient Note: The heart icon uses gradients. To replicate this, the style should mix the Cyan and Green with a slight "glossy" or "3D vector" finish.

2. The Style Analysis
Mood: Trustworthy, Professional, Caring, Clean, Modern, Hygienic.

Typography Style: Modern Sans-Serif (Geometric but with humanistic/rounded touches).

Graphic Style: Minimalist vector art, organic curves (specifically the "heart" shape), ample white space.